OL,3,CWhere to get help if you are suffering
OL,4,Cwith domestic abuse
OL,6,FIf you are a victim of domestic abuse
OL,7,Fin the North East or the wider UK,
OL,8,Fthere are a number of ways you can get
OL,9,Fhelp - including making a silent 999
OL,10,Fphone call.
OL,12,FImmediate danger help
OL,14,FAnyone who is in immediate risk of
OL,15,Fbeing harmed is advised to call 999.
