OL,3,CWhere to get help if you are suffering
OL,4,Cwith domestic abuse
OL,6,FIf they are unable to speak, the
OL,7,F'Silent Solution system' enables a 999
OL,8,Fmobile caller who is too scared to
OL,9,Fmake a noise, or speak, when prompted
OL,10,Fby the call handler, to press 55 to
OL,11,Finform police they are in a genuine
OL,12,Femergency.
OL,14,FWhile the police will not be able to
OL,15,Ftrack your mobile phone's location by
OL,16,Fpressing 55 during the phone call, it
OL,17,Fwill let the phone operator know that
OL,18,Fthis is not a hoax call and you will
OL,19,Fbe put through to the police.
