OL,6,FThose worried about someone else (such
OL,7,Fas a family member, friend, neighbour
OL,8,For colleague) can contact Findaway on
OL,9,F0300 140 0061 or visit
OL,10,Fwww.wefindaway.org.uk
OL,12,FHelp for women from minority
OL,13,Fbackgrounds
OL,15,FThe Angelou Centre in Newcastle upon
OL,16,FTyne can help arrange refuge
OL,17,Faccommodation.
